channel.title: String Dump
channel.description:
Dump includes the indexes and text for the words on interfaces. If you want to look up text such as the log-out button's just search for the text in this file to find the index as well. Could be useful if you want to use packet 126 to manually change text server sided.
http://uppit.com/kdkxrmr8t2hb/Text_Dump.txt
Example of the format:
[code] 2450 - When you have finished playing 2451 - RuneScape, always use the 2452 - button below to logout safely. 2458 - Click here to logout [/code]
